<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٤ - <span class="c3">{وَيْلٌ لِكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ}</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{اَلْحُطَمَةِ}</span>: اسْمُ النَّارِ،<span class="c5"> مِثْلُ:</span> سَقَرَ وَلَظَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(والهُمزة)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قوله:</span> <span class="c2">(قال يحيى)</span>؛<span class="c5"> أي:</span> الفَرَّاء صاحب كتاب <span class="c1">"مَعاني القُرآن"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(الحطمة)</span>؛<span class="c5"> أي:</span> لأنها تَكسِر،<span class="c5"> أي:</span> تَحطِم، وما ذُكر فيها من التفسير كلُّه ظاهرٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>* * *<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٠٥ - <span class="c3">{أَلَم تَرَ}</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{أبابيل}</span>: مُتَتَابِعَةً مُجْتَمِعَةً.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{مِن سِجِّيلٍ}</span> ": هِيَ سَنْكِ وَكِلْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
